    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-04-05T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-04-05T11:00:00-05:00" n="71"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d71">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.754/53: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Albania (<persName type="from"
                            >Bernstein</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tirana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-04-05T17:00:00+01:00"
                            >April 5, 1932—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 6:16 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. Naturalization treaty signed today omitting paragraph 3 of article number
                        1.<note n="2" xml:id="d71fn2">See text of unperfected treaty, signed January
                        21, 1931, <ref target="frus1931v01#pg_835">
                            <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, p. 835</ref>.</note> Signed treaty will be
                    delivered by me to the Department on my arrival at Washington.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bernstein</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
